{"tid":1465784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[事後檢討]希望大家注意多D敵人既內部分化","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:46:04.000Z","uid":52985,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd6af4645943d4893a48bc2f6964b79dcc13e87","tid":1465784,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"首先表明立場<br />\n不論勇武派定和理非做乜都好都唔會割蓆<br />\n最多好似而家咁事後檢討嫁姐<br />\n<br />\n今日機場發生左好多事<br />\n其實大部分都睇得出係政府經過琴日之後既部署黎<br />\n包括捉到公安/佔領離境出口/圍警察等等<br />\n好明顯都係因為政府唔想你地日日再咁圍機場既部署<br />\n主要係因為如果你和平咁圍,政府根本乜都做唔到<br />\n但只要有小小混亂,政府就會出師有名<br />\n令到之後落黎和理非怕亂唔敢再黎機場<br />\n等人愈黎愈少,圍機場既可能性就愈來愈低<br />\n始終大家要明白共產黨最叻唔係明刀明槍<br />\n而係係背後射暗箭,令你地內部分化,佢就不戰而勝<br />\n<br />\n今日好多事情都可以做得好D<br />\n例如捉到鬼唔洗下下都打死佢既<br />\n中佢2野之後有救護黎咪放佢囉<br />\n你唔放人班黑警衝入黎咪仲煩<br />\n圍離境我覺得冇乜問題<br />\n但可能做得好D<br />\n例如出面好多巴打提議既讓返一條路出黎<br />\n再配合道歉運動相信旅客會明白既<br />\n<br />\n要記住係機場,只要冇任何事發生<br />\n每日咁圍落去我地嬴面只會愈來愈高<br />\n重點要放係點樣確保呢個運動可以日復日咁進行<br />\n而唔係希望無啦啦有咩突破<br />\n只要圍多幾日HSI 好快見1字頭嫁喇<br />\n<br />\n雖然我平時D POST都冇乜人回<br />\n我又唔太識講野同分析<br />\n希望大家睇到同意又好唔同意都好<br />\n都唔好再比人分化到<br />\n記住共產黨只係會怕一樣野:團結"},{"pid":"316657c025d3d13a530c0ec6c82b42ff5919602e","tid":1465784,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b591ea657f8d77fa5875a0fe1640402f9bb958","tid":1465784,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"希望勇武派記住<br />\n機場係以和理非做主導<br />\n有陣時忍下手唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f984f00b72cec5cd3c947283be6ee082cc3330a3","tid":1465784,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba18206644998a9390f6524ffe1bf06c6985233","tid":1465784,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7d6db3ac74d89a944cf9bb7ce1d68c491efd40","tid":1465784,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62be16fad4829c0baf937499067e5e6fc225b318","tid":1465784,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60a9251da17774c59c768653c30dc25766e48ff","tid":1465784,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}